data.description: Beautiful custom built home on a 2.000 Acre lot, heavily covered in cedar trees. Split floorpan with large master bath and walk-in master closet. Jack and jill bath splits the other two bedrooms along with a half bath for guests. Fourth bedroom or bonus room and third bath added above garage during construction. This home will boast heavy farm-style trim-work, foa beams, and beautiful cabinets. Contract early enough and add some of your own touches.  Info to be verified by purchaser.
